message: #8703 Sometimes I really dislike some of my sisters (especially those on exec) and think about de-affiliating, but then I remember there are some sisters that I have grown so close to that I can't imagine my life without them <3

#8698 It might be hard and scary right now, but try to remember that there is at least someone out there who is thinking of you. You are loved. You matter. Don't let anybody tell you that you don't. We'll get through this together, ok? Thank you for being you.
